titles.title: To provide for the liquidation or reliquidation of certain frozen concentrated orange juice entries to correct an error that was made in connection with the original liquidation.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.

bill.summary: 6/24/1996--Introduced. Directs the U.S. Customs Service to liquidate or reliquidate (refund the duties on) certain entries of frozen concentrated orange juice.
